#slide[
  = LLVM <llvm>

  LLVM is a collection of modular and reusable compiler and toolchain technologies.

  - *Frontend*: Translates source code to LLVM IR (e.g., Clang, rustc).
  - *Optimizer*: Performs hardware-independent optimizations on IR.
  - *Backend*: Translates IR to machine code for specific architectures (X86, ARM, RISC-V).
]
